com.sun.pdfview

类 PDFImage.JpegDecoder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.pdfview.PDFImage.JpegDecoder
  • 封闭类:
    PDFImage

    private class PDFImage.JpegDecoder
extends java.lang.Object
    Decodes jpeg data, possibly attempting a manual YCCK decode if requested. Users should use getColorModel() to see which color model should now be used after a successful decode.

    • 方法详细资料

      • setYcckDecodeMode

        public void setYcckDecodeMode(boolean ycckDecodeMode)
        Identify whether the decoder should operate in YCCK decode mode, whereby the YCCK Chroma is specifically looked for and the color model is changed to support converting raw YCCK color values, working around a lack of YCCK/CMYK report in the standard Java jpeg readers. Non-YCCK images will not be decoded while in this mode.
        参数:
        ycckDecodeMode -
